<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hukdampa Mun Siem</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampan mun a siem zotai,
 Gitloh a puksa thokit in;
 La sa kawmin zuon hitiu,
 Ei tatna a bukim zo tai.

[V2]
 Ei hehpihna lultak ziek chun,
 Chawl ingka, Ka Pa gam achun;
 Kumsawtin a vakah leng ingka.

[V3]
 2. I umnau lei in mauna hi,
 Sie mah lele kumsawt In ding;
 Eihaw a dingin A siem,
 Gimthei chate I nunnawp nan.

[V4]
 3. &quot;Kuole ka kawma hungta chu,
 Nawhdawk puong ka&quot; na tih ziekin;
 Gitlohna tawh ka hunzuon,
 Aw Lalpa, ei hih thiengtho in.

[V5]
 4. Khensate chu ngai mah leng le,
 Lalpa gamah tuokkit hitiu;
 Nei hehpihna Aw nem chun,
 Tuhin Lalpa'n ei lungmuon hi.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>205</hymn_number>
</song>